# Week 3 Mini Project — `FinalLogProcessor.java`

Build this from scratch. No looking at previous files.

**Target output:**
```
=== SENTINEL LOG PROCESSOR ===

System initializing...
Check #1 complete.
Check #2 complete.
Check #3 complete. System ready.

Processing 50 logs...

[ERROR] PaymentService | Log #3 — ALERT SENT
[ERROR] AuthService | Log #6 — ALERT SENT
[ERROR] PaymentService | Log #9 — ALERT SENT
[ERROR] AuthService | Log #12 — ALERT SENT
[ERROR] PaymentService | Log #15 — ALERT SENT
CRITICAL detected at Log #20 — halting scan.

=== FINAL REPORT ===
Total processed: 20
Errors found: 5
INFO skipped: 6
System status: DEGRADED
```

**Rules — figure out HOW yourself:**
- `do-while` → 3 system checks before ready DONE
- `for` loop → process up to 50 logs
- `continue` → skip INFO logs
- `break` → stop at first CRITICAL
- Alternate services every other log
- Every 3rd log = ERROR, every 4th = CRITICAL, every 5th = INFO, rest = WARN
- Count errors, skipped, total processed
- Status = DEGRADED if errors > 0, else HEALTHY

